  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of harmonic scalpel and ligasure devices in laparoscopic morbid obesity surgery
      especially in gastric bypass surgery patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' department performs 150 gastric bypass surgeries annually. Surgeons use
      both harmonic scalpel and ligasure sealing device in cases. Aim is to compare both of these
      devices over coming each other. Benefits ease of these devices are compared.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
